	<div class="tve-cb" data-css="tve-u-1818939ea32" style=""><div class="thrv_wrapper thrv_text_element kbm8a9n0 dynamic-group-kbm8ujng" data-css="tve-u-1818939ea33" style=""><p style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 17px !important; text-align: center;"><strong>當顧客登入時或訪客進入到我們購物網站並完成註冊後，Header 呈現如下：</strong></p></div><div class="thrv_wrapper tve_image_caption" data-css="tve-u-18185f3e175" style=""><span class="tve_image_frame"><img decoding="async" class="tve_image tcb-moved-image wp-image-4191" alt="Header_編輯主選單_Custom_menu_completed_login" data-id="4191" width="684" data-init-width="1657" height="71" data-init-height="171" title="Header_編輯主選單_Custom_menu_completed_login" loading="lazy" src="/images/courses/ecommerce-setup/Header_編輯主選單_Custom_menu_completed_login-min.png" data-width="684" data-height="71" style="aspect-ratio: auto 1657 / 171;" data-css="tve-u-18185f3b7a0" srcset="https://mymerrylife.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Header_編輯主選單_Custom_menu_completed_login-min.png 1657w, https://mymerrylife.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Header_編輯主選單_Custom_menu_completed_login-min-300x31.png 300w, https://mymerrylife.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Header_編輯主選單_Custom_menu_completed_login-min-1024x106.png 1024w, https://mymerrylife.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Header_編輯主選單_Custom_menu_completed_login-min-768x79.png 768w, https://mymerrylife.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Header_編輯主選單_Custom_menu_completed_login-min-1536x159.png 1536w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 684px) 100vw, 684px" /></span></div></div>
